    ns1:evaluationDescription """The evaluation criterion to be followed is Progressive Assessment and for this purpose, 4 exams have been arranged, which constitute 25% of the weight of the mark.
Those who do not follow this type of evaluation must express it at the beginning of the course and only the Final Evaluation of the subject will be carried out in Week 17th."""@es ;
